{"day":4,"topic":{"title":"Be Verb","emoji":"🔤","cefr":"A1","difficulty":"beginner","type":"grammar"},"content":{"explanation":"\n**Be Verb — am/is/are/was/were:**\n\n\"Be\" verb English ki sabse important verb hai!\nIske bina koi sentence complete nahi hota.\n\n**Present:**\n| Subject | Be Verb |\n|---------|---------|\n| I       | am      |\n| He/She/It | is   |\n| You/We/They | are |\n\n**Past:**\n| Subject | Be Verb |\n|---------|---------|\n| I/He/She/It | was |\n| You/We/They | were |\n  ","rules":["I → am (always, no exception)","He/She/It + singular noun → is","You/We/They + plural noun → are","Past singular (I/He/She/It) → was","Past plural (You/We/They) → were","Question: Am/Is/Are + subject + ...?","Negative: subject + am/is/are + not"],"memoryTrick":"**\"Am I? Is he? Are they?\" — AIA = A I A** याद रखो:\n• \"A\"m — I\n• \"I\"s — He/She/It\n• \"A\"re — You/We/They","examples":[{"hindi":"मैं खुश हूँ।","english":"I am happy.","type":"am + adjective"},{"hindi":"वह एक डॉक्टर है।","english":"He is a doctor.","type":"is + profession"},{"hindi":"हम भारतीय हैं।","english":"We are Indians.","type":"are + nationality"},{"hindi":"मैं कल बीमार था।","english":"I was sick yesterday.","type":"was + adjective (past)"},{"hindi":"वे कल यहाँ थे।","english":"They were here yesterday.","type":"were + place (past)"},{"hindi":"क्या तुम तैयार हो?","english":"Are you ready?","type":"Question"}],"mistakes":[{"wrong":"I is a student.","correct":"I am a student.","why":"I के साथ हमेशा \"am\""},{"wrong":"He are a teacher.","correct":"He is a teacher.","why":"He के साथ \"is\""},{"wrong":"They was happy.","correct":"They were happy.","why":"They के साथ \"were\" (past)"},{"wrong":"She were at home.","correct":"She was at home.","why":"She के साथ \"was\" (past)"}],"speakingTips":["Daily describe yourself: \"I am [adjective] today because...\"","Describe others around you in English","Weather, feelings, locations — be verb se sab describe hota hai"]},"vocabulary":[{"id":1,"word":"Tired","hindi":"थका हुआ","ipa":"","example":"I am tired after work."},{"id":2,"word":"Confident","hindi":"आत्मविश्वासी","ipa":"","example":"She is very confident."},{"id":3,"word":"Excited","hindi":"उत्साहित","ipa":"","example":"We are excited about the trip."},{"id":4,"word":"Nervous","hindi":"घबराया हुआ","ipa":"","example":"He was nervous in the interview."},{"id":5,"word":"Proud","hindi":"गर्वित","ipa":"","example":"I am proud of you."},{"id":6,"word":"Disappointed","hindi":"निराश","ipa":"","example":"She was disappointed with results."},{"id":7,"word":"Enthusiastic","hindi":"उत्साही","ipa":"","example":"They are enthusiastic learners."},{"id":8,"word":"Determined","hindi":"दृढ़ निश्चयी","ipa":"","example":"You are very determined."}],"practice":[{"id":"d04-001","hindi":"मैं थका हुआ हूँ।","english":"I am tired.","alternatives":["i am exhausted."],"hint":"I am + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-002","hindi":"वह एक डॉक्टर है।","english":"He is a doctor.","alternatives":["she is a doctor."],"hint":"He/She is a + profession","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-003","hindi":"हम खुश हैं।","english":"We are happy.","alternatives":["we are glad."],"hint":"We are + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-004","hindi":"यह किताब अच्छी है।","english":"This book is good.","alternatives":["this is a good book."],"hint":"This + is + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-005","hindi":"वे तैयार हैं।","english":"They are ready.","alternatives":["they are prepared."],"hint":"They are + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-006","hindi":"मैं कल बीमार था।","english":"I was sick yesterday.","alternatives":["i was ill yesterday."],"hint":"Was = past of am/is","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-007","hindi":"वे कल ऑफिस में थे।","english":"They were in the office yesterday.","alternatives":["they were at office yesterday."],"hint":"Were = past of are","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-008","hindi":"क्या तुम ठीक हो?","english":"Are you okay?","alternatives":["are you alright?","are you fine?"],"hint":"Are you + adjective?","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-009","hindi":"मौसम बहुत गर्म है।","english":"The weather is very hot.","alternatives":["it is very hot."],"hint":"Weather + is + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-010","hindi":"वह मेरी दोस्त है।","english":"She is my friend.","alternatives":["she is my best friend."],"hint":"She is + my + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-011","hindi":"मैं एक छात्र हूँ।","english":"I am a student.","alternatives":["i am student."],"hint":"I am a + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-012","hindi":"यह घर बड़ा है।","english":"This house is big.","alternatives":["this house is large."],"hint":"This + noun + is + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-013","hindi":"क्या आप तैयार हैं?","english":"Are you ready?","alternatives":["are you prepared?"],"hint":"Are you + adjective?","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-014","hindi":"बाज़ार बंद था।","english":"The market was closed.","alternatives":["the shop was closed."],"hint":"Was = past singular","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-015","hindi":"वे बहुत व्यस्त थे।","english":"They were very busy.","alternatives":["they were quite busy."],"hint":"Were = past plural","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-016","hindi":"मेरे दोस्त होशियार हैं।","english":"My friends are intelligent.","alternatives":["my friends are smart.","my friends are clever."],"hint":"Plural + are + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-017","hindi":"खाना ठंडा है।","english":"The food is cold.","alternatives":["food is cold."],"hint":"Noun + is + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-018","hindi":"मैं गुस्से में नहीं हूँ।","english":"I am not angry.","alternatives":["i'm not angry.","i am not upset."],"hint":"I am not + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-019","hindi":"वह कहाँ है?","english":"Where is he?","alternatives":["where is she?"],"hint":"Where + is + subject?","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-020","hindi":"आसमान नीला है।","english":"The sky is blue.","alternatives":["sky is blue."],"hint":"Noun + is + color","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-021","hindi":"क्या तुम खुश हो?","english":"Are you happy?","alternatives":["are you glad?"],"hint":"Are you + adjective?","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-022","hindi":"हम सब भारतीय हैं।","english":"We are all Indians.","alternatives":["we all are indians."],"hint":"We are + all + nationality","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-023","hindi":"मेरा नाम गलत था।","english":"My name was wrong.","alternatives":["my name was incorrect."],"hint":"My name + was + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-024","hindi":"वह बहुत अच्छी इंसान है।","english":"She is a very good person.","alternatives":["she is a great person."],"hint":"She is a + adjective + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-025","hindi":"कमरे में 5 लोग हैं।","english":"There are 5 people in the room.","alternatives":["there are five people in the room."],"hint":"There are + number + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-026","hindi":"मेरी तबियत अच्छी नहीं है।","english":"I am not feeling well.","alternatives":["i am not well.","i do not feel good."],"hint":"I am not + well/feeling well","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-027","hindi":"वे सब पढ़े-लिखे हैं।","english":"They are all educated.","alternatives":["all of them are educated."],"hint":"They are all + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-028","hindi":"यह सच है।","english":"This is true.","alternatives":["it is true.","this is correct."],"hint":"This/It is + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-029","hindi":"उसकी बात सही थी।","english":"His point was correct.","alternatives":["his point was right.","what he said was correct."],"hint":"Noun + was + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-030","hindi":"बच्चे बहुत शरारती होते हैं।","english":"Children are very naughty.","alternatives":["kids are very naughty."],"hint":"Plural + are + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-031","hindi":"यह मेरा घर है।","english":"This is my house.","alternatives":["this is my home."],"hint":"This is + possessive + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d04-032","hindi":"हम कल व्यस्त थे।",